[normal] 
[normal]However, 
[normal]I do have a concern that fraud, and cyber enabled crime is increasing, and we do not have an accurate measurement of this as it is reported direct to Action Fraud. We have little feedback on the extent of it within Thames Valley, but I believe that, in monetary terms, it is by far the largest crime both within the Thames Valley Police area. I believe this to be the case nationally.
